<pb ed="T" id="T21.1277.0329b" n="0329b"/>
<lb n="0329b01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0329b02"/><head type="no">No. 1277</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0329b03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0329010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】保延三年寫高山寺藏本，【乙】高山寺藏三十帖策子轉寫本，【丙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，此經宋元二本俱缺</note>速疾立驗<note n="0329011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魔＝摩【明】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0329011"><lem>魔</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>醯首羅天<note n="0329012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">說＋（迦樓羅）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0329012"><lem>說</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">說迦樓羅</rdg></app>阿尾
<lb n="0329b04"/>奢法<note n="0329013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0329013"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0329b05"/>
<lb n="0329b06"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0329014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（開府…寺））三十七字＝（（唐北天竺））四字【明】【丙】，（（開府…門））四十一字＝（（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智））十一字【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0329014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門）四十一字＝（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智）十一字【甲】【乙】，（開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智大興善寺）三十七字＝（唐北天竺）四字【明】【丙】</note><app n="0329014"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0329b07"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0329b08"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙<note n="0329015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">門＋（大廣智）【明】【丙】</note><app n="0329015"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">門大廣智</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">唐北天竺三藏沙門</rdg></app>
<lb n="0329b09"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0329b10"/><p>爾時那羅延天。在於香醉山頂。請<app type="＊" source="0329011"><lem>魔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">摩</rdg></app>醯首羅
<lb n="0329b11"/>於自<note n="0329016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔在〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0329016"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>宮中。供養頭面禮足。白<app type="＊" source="0329011"><lem>魔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">摩</rdg></app>醯首羅
<lb n="0329b12"/>言。我所乘迦樓羅使者。能成辦世間所求事
<lb n="0329b13"/>要。<note n="0329017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">且＝但【丙】</note><app n="0329017"><lem>且</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">但</rdg></app>不能速疾。<note n="0329018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【明】【丙】</note><app n="0329018"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>願大天為未來有情。說
<lb n="0329b14"/>速疾立驗阿尾奢<note n="0329019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＋（爾）【丙】</note><app n="0329019"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">法爾</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0329b15"/><p>時<app type="＊" source="0329011"><lem>魔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">摩</rdg></app>醯首羅告那羅延言。汝當諦聽。我為汝
<lb n="0329b16"/>宣說速疾成辦使者之法。能作息災增益降
<lb n="0329b17"/>伏敬愛。亦能於夜<note n="0329020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＋（天）&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="0329020"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">摩天</rdg></app>界往來使役。能知未
<lb n="0329b18"/>來善惡吉凶成敗。旱澇不調&CB00444;國侵擾。惡人
<lb n="0329b19"/>叛亂種種災祥。若欲知未來事者。當簡擇四
<lb n="0329b20"/>五童男或童女。可年七八歲。身上無瘢痕<note n="0329021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02234;＝靨【明】【乙】，黶【丙】</note><note n="0329021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02234;＝靨【明】【乙】，＝黶【丙】</note><app n="0329021"><lem>&CB02234;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">靨</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">黶</rdg></app>
<lb n="0329b21"/>記。聰慧靈利。先令一七日服素食或三日食。
<lb n="0329b22"/>凡欲作法。要須吉日或鬼宿或歲宿直。甘露
<lb n="0329b23"/>直<note n="0329022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔直〕－【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0329022"><lem>直</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>日最勝。沐浴遍身塗香。著<note n="0329023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（新）＋淨【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0329023"><lem>淨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">新淨</rdg></app>衣口含
<lb n="0329b24"/>龍腦豆&CB03440;。持誦者面向東坐。身前以白檀香
<lb n="0329b25"/>塗一小壇。可一肘量。令童女等立於壇上。散
<lb n="0329b26"/>花於童女前。置一閼伽<note n="0329024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">爐＝嚴【明】，器【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0329024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">爐＝嚴【明】，＝器【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0329024"><lem>爐</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">嚴</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">器</rdg></app>取安息<note n="0329025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔香〕－【明】</note><app n="0329025"><lem>香</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。以大
<lb n="0329b27"/>印真言加持七遍。燒令童女熏手。又取赤花
<lb n="0329b28"/>加持七遍。安童女掌中。便以手掩面。則持誦
<lb n="0329b29"/>者結大印。<note n="0329026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（以）＋二【丙】</note><app n="0329026"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">以二</rdg></app>手合掌外相交。左押右虛其掌
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1277.0329c" n="0329c"/>
<lb n="0329c01"/>即成。以此印加持自身五處。所謂額右肩左
<lb n="0329c02"/>肩心喉。頂上散印即誦真言曰</p>
<lb n="0329c03"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0329027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曩謨＝娜莫【明】【丙】</note><app n="0329027"><lem>曩謨</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">娜莫</rdg></app>婆&CB00344;&CB00085;<note n="0329028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">底＋（一）夾註【明】【丙】</note><app n="0329028"><lem>底</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">底<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app><note n="0329029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【明】【丙】</note><app n="0329029"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>賀<note place="inline">引</note>母捺<note n="0329030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03307;＝&CB00942;【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0329030"><lem>&CB03307;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00942;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二<note n="0329031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（二）【明】【丙】</note><app n="0329031"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">合二</rdg></app></note>迦吒
<lb n="0329c04"/>&CB00256;施棄底哩<note place="inline">二合</note>施<anchor id="fxT21p0329c01"/><note n="0329032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03307;＝&CB00942;三【明】【丙】</note><app n="0329032"><lem>&CB03307;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00942;三</rdg></app>底哩<note place="inline">二合</note>路左<note n="0329033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00135;＋（四）夾註【明】【丙】</note><app n="0329033"><lem>&CB00135;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00135;<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app>伊
<lb n="0329c05"/>捨<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;跛輸<note n="0329034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跛＝跋【明】</note><app n="0329034"><lem>跛</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">跋</rdg></app>帝<note n="0329035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑＝薩【甲】＊</note><app n="0329035"><lem>娑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">薩</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline"><note n="0329036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＝五【明】【丙】</note><app n="0329036"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">五</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0329c06"/><p>則以此印按其童女頂。則想於頭上。三角赤
<lb n="0329c07"/>色熾盛火輪。<note n="0329037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（輝）＋光【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0329037"><lem>光</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">輝光</rdg></app>誦真言七遍。火輪真言曰</p>
<lb n="0329c08"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0329038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵＋（一）夾註【明】【丙】＊</note><app n="0329038"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>阿儗&CB00135;<note place="inline">二合</note>施棄<app type="＊" source="0329035"><lem>娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0329039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引二）細註【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0329039"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">賀<note place="inline">引二</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0329c09"/><p>則以此印按童女口上。於彼口中想水輪。白
<lb n="0329c10"/>色半月形。誦真言七遍。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0329c11"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0329038"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>惹&CB00256;祖哩<note place="inline">二合</note>拏<note place="inline">引</note>摩抳<app type="＊" source="0329035"><lem>娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0329040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引）【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0329040"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0329c12"/><p>次應移印按彼心中。想地輪形方黃色。誦七
<lb n="0329c13"/>遍真言曰</p>
<lb n="0329c14"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0329038"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>摩<note n="0329041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＝訶引【明】【丙】，賀引【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0329041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賀＝訶引【明】【丙】，＝賀引【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0329041"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">訶引</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">賀引</rdg></app>麼<note n="0329042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00256;＝囉【明】【丙】</note><app n="0329042"><lem>&CB00256;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app>跛囉訖囉<note place="inline">二合</note>摩<app type="＊" source="0329035"><lem>娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0329c15"/><app type="＊" source="0329040"><lem>賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0329c16"/><p>次應移印按彼臍中。想<note n="0329043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔風〕－【明】</note><app n="0329043"><lem>風</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>輪其形圓黑色。誦
<lb n="0329c17"/>七遍真言曰</p>
<lb n="0329c18"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0329038"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>尾曩多<note place="inline">引</note>句&CB00256;曩那<app type="＊" source="0329035"><lem>娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline"><note n="0329044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（二）【明】【丙】＊</note><app n="0329044"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">引二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0329c19"/><p>次應以大印加持彼兩&CB00560;。想迦樓羅誦<note n="0329045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（七遍）＋真【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0329045"><lem>真</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">七遍真</rdg></app>言
<lb n="0329c20"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0329c21"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0329038"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>跛乞史<note place="inline">二合</note>囉<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0329044"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">引二</rdg></app></note>惹跛那<app type="＊" source="0329035"><lem>娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline"><note n="0329046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（三）【明】【丙】</note><app n="0329046"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">引三</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0329c22"/><p>次應以大印誦甲冑真言。加持童女遍身旋
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1277.0330a" n="0330a"/>
<lb n="0330a01"/>轉。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0330a02"/><p type="dharani"><app type="＊" source="0329038"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>迦&CB00085;左<note n="0330001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＋（賀）【甲】【乙】，（賀引）【丙】</note><app n="0330001"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">摩賀</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">摩賀引</rdg></app>部<note place="inline">引</note>多<note n="0330002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】</note><app n="0330002"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>地跛帝<app type="＊" source="0329035"><lem>娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0330a03"/><note n="0330003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引）【乙】</note><app n="0330003"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0330a04"/><p>行者次應自身為<app type="＊" source="0329011"><lem>魔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">摩</rdg></app>醯首羅天。三目頭冠瓔
<lb n="0330a05"/>珞莊嚴。頭冠上有佛半月。<note n="0330004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">項＝頂【丙】</note><app n="0330004"><lem>項</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">頂</rdg></app>上青。十八臂。
<lb n="0330a06"/>手持種種器仗。以龍為<note n="0330005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">紳＝神【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330005"><lem>紳</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">神</rdg></app>線。角絡繫。又<note n="0330006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彼＝披【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330006"><lem>彼</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">披</rdg></app>
<lb n="0330a07"/>塗血<note n="0330007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寫及＝象皮【明】【乙】【丙】，寫皮【甲】</note><note n="0330007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寫及＝象皮【明】【乙】【丙】，＝寫皮【甲】</note><app n="0330007"><lem>寫及</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">象皮</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">寫皮</rdg></app>。須臾頃觀自身已。次應以大印護
<lb n="0330a08"/>彼童女一百八命節。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0330a09"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note><note n="0330008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜜＝密【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330008"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">密</rdg></app>哩<note place="inline">二合</note>體尾<note n="0330009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">野＝也【甲】＊</note><app n="0330009"><lem>野</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">也</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>吒多<note place="inline"><note n="0330010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（二合）＋二【明】＊</note><app n="0330010"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">二合二</rdg></app></note>惹<note n="0330011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縛＝&CB00085;【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0330011"><lem>縛</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0330a10"/><note n="0330012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">揄＝榆【明】【乙】</note><app n="0330012"><lem>揄</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">榆</rdg></app>囉迦<note n="0330013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">苫＝苦三【明】</note><app n="0330013"><lem>苫</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">苦三</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0330a11"/><p>結其大印及誦真言。遍身旋繞加持。則護<note n="0330014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一百〕－【明】</note><app n="0330014"><lem>一
<lb n="0330a12"/>百</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>八種命節</p>
<lb n="0330a13"/><p>次又以大印。真言加持花香及閼伽等</p>
<lb n="0330a14"/><p><note n="0330015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔次〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0330015"><lem>次</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>又以大印真言結十方界。則應對此童女
<lb n="0330a15"/>前。誦<app type="＊" source="0329011"><lem>魔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">摩</rdg></app>醯首羅使者真言曰</p>
<lb n="0330a16"/><p type="dharani">唎躋吒迦<note place="inline">一</note>麼多那<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;<note place="inline">二</note>尾灑娜<note n="0330016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跛＝跋【明】＊</note><app n="0330016"><lem>跛</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">跋</rdg></app>拏<note place="inline">三</note>薩
<lb n="0330a17"/>摩那&CB00344;囉<note place="inline">四</note>尾訖囉<note place="inline">二合</note>摩<note place="inline">五</note>尾羅<note place="inline">引</note>薩&CB00344;底<note place="inline">六</note>
<lb n="0330a18"/>&CB00074;濟吒迦<note place="inline">七</note>布囉<note place="inline">二合</note>哩<app type="＊" source="0330016"><lem>跛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">跋</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>擔&CB00772;<note place="inline">二合八</note>左<note n="0330017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【明】【丙】＊</note><app n="0330017"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app>
