<lb n="0330a20"/><app type="＊" source="0330016"><lem>跛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">跋</rdg></app>尼<note place="inline">十二</note>伴<note n="0330019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上〕－【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330019"><lem><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>爾伴爾<note place="inline">十三</note>羯恥羯恥<note place="inline">十四</note>阿
<lb n="0330a21"/>尾捨阿尾捨<note place="inline">十五</note>&CB00074;躋吒迦<note place="inline">十六</note>嚕奴<note n="0330020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">噌＝嚕【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0330020"><lem>噌</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">嚕</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0330a22"/><note n="0330021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00242;＝枳【明】【甲】</note><app n="0330021"><lem>&CB00242;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">枳</rdg></app>孃<note place="inline">二合</note>跋野<note n="0330022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">底＋（十七）夾註【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330022"><lem>底</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">底<note place="inline">十七</note></rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0329035"><lem>娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note n="0330023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十七引〕－【甲】</note><app n="0330023"><lem><note place="inline">十<note n="0330024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">七＝八【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330024"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">八</rdg></app>引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0330a23"/><p>此真言應誦七遍。則彼童女戰動。當知聖者
<lb n="0330a24"/>入身。則更彈指誦真言。若無現驗。次誦<note n="0330025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摧＝催【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330025"><lem>摧</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">催</rdg></app>
<lb n="0330a25"/>迫使者真言曰</p>
<lb n="0330a26"/><p type="dharani">&CB00074;&CB00074;耶<note place="inline">一</note>摩<note n="0330026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魯＝嚕【明】【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0330026"><lem>魯</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">嚕</rdg></app>呬多<note place="inline"><note n="0330027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二引＝引二【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330027"><lem>二引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">引二</rdg></app></note>素囉素囉<note place="inline"><note n="0330028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三引＝引三【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330028"><lem>三引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">引三</rdg></app></note>布
<lb n="0330a27"/>爾多賀那賀那<note place="inline">四</note><note n="0330029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波＝沒【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330029"><lem>波</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">沒</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾麼<note place="inline">二合<note n="0330030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＝五【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330030"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">五</rdg></app></note>那尼
<lb n="0330a28"/><note n="0330031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔五〕－【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330031"><lem><note place="inline">五</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>那&CB00418;嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>尼<note n="0330032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">都＝&CB00418;【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330032"><lem>都</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00418;</rdg></app>嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>尼<note place="inline">六</note>謨尼謨尼<note place="inline">七</note>
<lb n="0330a29"/>伴<note place="inline"><note n="0330033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】【丙】＊</note><app n="0330033"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">上聲</rdg></app></note>爾伴<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0330033"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">上聲</rdg></app></note>爾<note place="inline">八</note>羯恥羯恥<note place="inline">九</note>阿尾<note n="0330034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捨＝舍【明】【丙】＊</note><app n="0330034"><lem>捨</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">舍</rdg></app>阿尾
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1277.0330b" n="0330b"/>
<lb n="0330b01"/><app type="＊" source="0330034"><lem>捨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">舍</rdg></app><note place="inline">十</note>&CB00074;躋吒迦<note place="inline">十一</note>嚕奴<app type="＊" source="0330020"><lem>噌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">嚕</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>枳孃<note place="inline">二合</note>跛
<lb n="0330b02"/>野帝<note n="0330035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十二〕－【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330035"><lem><note place="inline">十二</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0329035"><lem>娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline"><note n="0330036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">十三引＝引十二【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330036"><lem>十三引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">引十二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0330b03"/><p>誦此真言必速應驗。問未來善惡一切災<note n="0330037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祥＋（事）【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330037"><lem>祥</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">祥事</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0330b04"/>若不語或語遲。則結棒印</p>
<lb n="0330b05"/><p>二手合掌。二無名指外<note n="0330038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">支＝叉【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330038"><lem>支</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">叉</rdg></app>。二中指並立。二
<lb n="0330b06"/>頭指各鉤無名指頭。二大指各令押中交。誦
<lb n="0330b07"/>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0330b08"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>母那&CB00344;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0330010"><lem>二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">二合二</rdg></app></note>都嚕都嚕<note place="inline">三</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀
<lb n="0330b09"/><note n="0330039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引四〕－【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330039"><lem><note place="inline">引四</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0330b10"/><p>結此棒印。則<note n="0330040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">語＝諮【丙】</note><app n="0330040"><lem>語</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">諮</rdg></app>問種種事已。以大印真言加
<lb n="0330b11"/>持閼伽。三灑童女面。即結解。此使者真言
<lb n="0330b12"/>先應誦一萬遍則法成。則見身來。須獻閼伽
<lb n="0330b13"/>乞願。願聖者一切處一切時使用皆辦。則隱
<lb n="0330b14"/>不現。已後欲使。塗一小壇著香花飲食。誦真
<lb n="0330b15"/>言一百八遍。則現身。則言龍宮中取長年藥
<lb n="0330b16"/>如意寶珠。或使夜摩王處。延命增益壽命。或
<lb n="0330b17"/>使<note n="0330041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（天）＋上【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330041"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">天上</rdg></app>取妙甘露。或使他國問其善惡。亦能助
<lb n="0330b18"/>軍陣摧破他敵。種種使用悉能成辦。此法一
<lb n="0330b19"/>切迦樓羅法中最殊勝。祕密難得。汝當揀擇
<lb n="0330b20"/>法器堪傳授者而傳與。<note n="0330042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">非人器人＝之若傳非器人【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330042"><lem>非人器人</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">之若傳非器人</rdg></app>即損他。已
<lb n="0330b21"/>後此法不成。是故應極祕密勿妄傳<note n="0330043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝授【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330043"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">授</rdg></app>之。大
<lb n="0330b22"/>自在天迦樓羅陀羅尼曰</p>
<lb n="0330b23"/><p type="dharani">那謨婆伽&CB00085;底<note place="inline">一</note>嚕馱囉野<note place="inline">二</note>瞋那劫波<note n="0330044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝&CB00256;【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330044"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00256;</rdg></app>野
<lb n="0330b24"/><note place="inline">三</note>薩&CB00085;微那延迦囉<app type="＊" source="0330009"><lem>野</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">也</rdg></app><note place="inline">四</note>薩&CB00085;羯摩莎馱那
<lb n="0330b25"/><app type="＊" source="0330009"><lem>野</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">也</rdg></app><note place="inline">五</note>薩&CB00085;&CB00085;尸迦<app type="＊" source="0330017"><lem>羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">囉</rdg></app><note n="0330045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拏＋（二合）夾註【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330045"><lem>拏</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">拏<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>野<note place="inline">六</note>薩&CB00085;設<note n="0330046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00418;＝都【明】【乙】</note><app n="0330046"><lem>&CB00418;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">都</rdg></app>嚕
<lb n="0330b26"/><note place="inline">二合</note>尾那捨那野<note place="inline">七</note>唵<note n="0330047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔八〕－【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330047"><lem><note place="inline">八</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>迦波羅質擔瞋<note n="0330048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那＋（入聲八）夾註【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330048"><lem>那</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">那<note place="inline">入聲八</note></rdg></app>迦
<lb n="0330b27"/>波羅部擔<note n="0330049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔九〕－【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330049"><lem><note place="inline">九</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>嚕訥嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>枳孃<note place="inline">二合</note><app type="＊" source="0330016"><lem>跛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">跋</rdg></app><note n="0330050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">野＝哩【明】，也【甲】</note><note n="0330050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">野＝哩【明】，＝也【甲】</note><app n="0330050"><lem>野</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">哩</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">也</rdg></app>帝
<lb n="0330b28"/><note n="0330051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十〕－【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330051"><lem><note place="inline">十</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0329035"><lem>娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0330052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引九）夾註【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330052"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">賀<note place="inline">引九</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0330b29"/><p>此陀羅尼。調伏人取<note n="0330053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">赤＋（色）【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330053"><lem>赤</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">赤色</rdg></app>芭蕉葉畫彼人。心上
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1277.0330c" n="0330c"/>
<lb n="0330c01"/>書名字。誦陀羅尼一百八遍。即埋牛糞中即
<lb n="0330c02"/>調伏。欲令&CB00594;子對相憎。多羅葉畫彼男女形。
<lb n="0330c03"/>書名相背。取線<note n="0330054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">纏＝繫【明】</note><app n="0330054"><lem>纏</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">繫</rdg></app>。取鼠狼毛山&CB00470;毛蛇退皮
<lb n="0330c04"/>燒熏。誦陀羅尼一百八遍。安劫波羅中。即於
<lb n="0330c05"/>屍林中埋著。便相憎。除&CB00230;依舊。若令相憐者。
<lb n="0330c06"/>還於多羅葉上畫彼<note n="0330055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夫＝人【明】，夫＋（妻）【丙】</note><app n="0330055"><lem>夫</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">夫妻</rdg></app>形。書名相合。取白線
<lb n="0330c07"/>繫。取雀兒毛蛇皮燒熏。誦陀羅尼一百八遍。
<lb n="0330c08"/>即相憐</p>
<lb n="0330c09"/><p>又法欲令人相打。於大<note n="0330056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">虫＝蟲【明】</note><app n="0330056"><lem>虫</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">蟲</rdg></app>皮或於牛皮。畫二
<lb n="0330c10"/>人相把頭髻。書名著。取線纏著。於火上<note n="0330057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">重＝熏【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0330057"><lem>重</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">熏</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0330c11"/>埋碓臼下。即得日日相打。除劫止</p>
<lb n="0330c12"/><p>又法若欲調伏人者。取貝多葉上畫人形。書
<lb n="0330c13"/>名誦陀羅尼一百八遍。即於床下埋。即得調
<lb n="0330c14"/>伏</p>
<lb n="0330c15"/><p>又法令尿血者。取多羅葉畫彼人。書姓名。取
<lb n="0330c16"/>釘誦陀羅尼一百八遍。釘上七七日。即得除
<lb n="0330c17"/>去</p>
<lb n="0330c18"/><p>次說眼藥法。若調伏&CB00594;子者。取蛇頭竭羅安
<lb n="0330c19"/>善那青木香<note n="0330058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寫＝象【明】【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0330058"><lem>寫</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">象</rdg></app>甲蜂二<note n="0330059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">介＝箇【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330059"><lem>介</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">箇</rdg></app>。於黑月十四日
<lb n="0330c20"/>擣作<note n="0330060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">抹＝末【明】【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0330060"><lem>抹</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">末</rdg></app>。和肉點眼角。一切&CB00594;子隨逐。天上
<lb n="0330c21"/>亦來非但人<note n="0330061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">間＝聞&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="0330061"><lem>間</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">聞</rdg></app><note n="0330062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也＋（阿尾奢法）細註【明】【丙】</note><app n="0330062"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">也<note place="inline">阿尾奢法</note></rdg></app></p>
